graph TB
    subgraph "KubeRay Component"
        Operator[KubeRay Operator<br/>Port: 8080/TCP metrics<br/>Port: 8081/TCP health]
        APIServer[KubeRay API Server<br/>Optional<br/>Port: 8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Port: 8887/TCP gRPC]
        Operator -.->|optional| APIServer
    end

    subgraph "Ray Cluster Resources"
        RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
        RayJobCR[RayJob CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
        RayServiceCR[RayService CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Ray Cluster Infrastructure"
        HeadPod[Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS: 6379/TCP<br/>Dashboard: 8265/TCP<br/>Client: 10001/TCP<br/>Serve: 8000/TCP]
        WorkerPods[Ray Worker Pods<br/>Autoscaling 0-N replicas]
        Autoscaler[Ray Autoscaler<br/>Sidecar in Head Pod]

        HeadPod -->|sidecar| Autoscaler
        HeadPod -->|GCS coordination| WorkerPods
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| RayClusterCR
    User -->|creates| RayJobCR
    User -->|creates| RayServiceCR

    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| Operator
    RayJobCR -->|watched by| Operator
    RayServiceCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates & manages| HeadPod
    Operator -->|creates & manages| WorkerPods
    Operator -->|creates| Services[Kubernetes Services<br/>head-svc, serve-svc]
    Operator -->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>Optional for external access]

    APIServer -->|manages via K8s API| RayClusterCR
    APIServer -->|manages via K8s API| RayJobCR
    APIServer -->|manages via K8s API| RayServiceCR

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]
        Redis[External Redis<br/>Optional GCS FT<br/>6379/TCP]
        Registry[Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        S3[S3/Cloud Storage<br/>Optional<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Operator -->|watches & manages| K8sAPI
    Operator -->|pulls images| Registry
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| Operator
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| HeadPod
    HeadPod -.->|GCS fault tolerance| Redis
    HeadPod -.->|checkpoints & state| S3

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style APIServer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HeadPod fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style WorkerPods fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Autoscaler fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayClusterCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayJobCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Redis fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Registry fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333
